These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, rowing, snowboarding, lacrosse
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, oliveros, swisher, havana
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, march, may, november
There are 4 different nationalities: german, japanese, colombian, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, horse, mouse
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the havana-smoker is on the left of the japanese##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the german is the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the japanese is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the colombian is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's sport is handball##1
10. the owner of the horse is the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport          | rowing    | snowboarding      | handball  | lacrosse     |
| Cigar         | havana    | swisher   | vegafina | oliveros      |
| Birthday   | march       | october | may     | november    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | japanese         | german  | colombian    |
| Pet           | horse      | mouse       | chinchilla | guinea-pig |

