.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, car, taxi, tram
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, japanese, spanish, chinese
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, collecting, gardening, baking
4 different games are played: scrabble, whist, monopoly, domino
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, skiing
 1. the japanese is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the turkish##1
 8. the person playing whist is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 9. the spanish is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Transport      | car      | motorbike     | taxi    | tram |
| Nationality   | turkish | japanese   | spanish   | chinese           |
| Hobby   | collecting  | baking     | gardening    | photography         |
| Game           | domino         | whist | monopoly     | scrabble        |
| Sport         | cricket     | skiing  | handball | parkour       |

