House: palace, colonial, victorian, cottage
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, lemonade, almond-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, tram, trike
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is the cottage house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 6. the person driving the trike is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the game-smoker is the colonial house##1
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the victorian house##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the victorian house##1
12. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Birthday          | april    | october      | july  | september   |
| Cigar   | game     | cain      | old-henry | aristoff      |
