 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 3. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 7. the modern house is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the palace house##1
 9. the tower house is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
11. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
12. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Flower      | lily   | orchid   | dahlia      | sunflower     |
| Hobby          | skydiving     | dancing   | chess | card-games |
