.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis, sunflower, azalea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, cycling, soccer, skateboarding
4 different games are played: canasta, chess, billiard, go
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, game, havana, bluemaster
 1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the game-smoker##1
10. the person drinking water is the person playing chess##1
11. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | coffee     | hot-chocolate  | water       | mirinda      |
| Flower       | sunflower    | azalea        | balloon-flower  | amaryllis      |
| Sport         | cycling  | skateboarding | rugby | soccer |
| Game         | canasta | go          | chess         | billiard      |
| Cigar   | game     | montecristo     | havana       | bluemaster          |

