.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, climbing, cricket, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, roller, boat
4 different games are played: go, whist, domino, monopoly
City: nizza, berlin, colone, paris
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, rat, snake
 1. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 5. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 6. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the person playing domino##1
10. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Sport      | sailing       | cricket      | climbing      | handball    |
| Transport         | boat | roller | snowmobile | scooter  |
| Game   | domino    | whist     | monopoly      | go |
| City   | colone  | paris     | nizza    | berlin  |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | snake       | cat          | rat      |

