.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, metal, soul, disco
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, daffodil, tulip
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, july, june
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, chestnut, green, apricot
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the person who likes green is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 6. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 7. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the fan of metal##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is the fan of soul##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the fan of disco##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
