The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, funk, disco
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship, snowmobile
 1. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who likes brown##1
 2. the fan of funk is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 5. the fan of funk is the person who likes mauve##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the davidoff-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person playing whist is on the right of the fan of country##1
10. the person playing go is the fan of disco##1
11. the fan of disco is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the fan of disco is on the left of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
