| Game        | canasta    | go        | monopoly        | whist      |
| Color       | ivory       | brown       | amber      | mauve |
| Cigar         | bongani | pall-mall | blend | davidoff      |
| Music-Genre         | blues          | disco         | country           | funk    |
| Transport   | ship         | scooter       | snowmobile     | motorbike   |

 